name: Pharah (Overwatch) LORA
description:
Tried my best to make sure flying poses and gun weren't too hard to prompt, hopefully it worked. Pure Pharah prompt should already give full look including armor, but if not - use outfit triggers.

blurry, blurry background, blurry foreground in negative prompt recommended.

Checked strength range is 0.6-0.8. Triggers for paticular things are:

  • Outfit - armor, armored boots, full armor, power armor, full power armor, mechanical arms, gauntlets, pelvic curtain, thrusters

  • Accesories - mechanical wings, justicerain, missile, fire, helmet, holding helmet, headgear removed, condensation trail, sunglasses

  • Gun - holding gun, weapon, assault rifle, energy gun

If you liked my work, you can donate here.

Trained on Anything V4.5 with anime.vae.

Samples are 512x768\768x512, not cherry picked, without HighRes.fix, using OrangeCocoa 50/50 Mix , with OrangeMix VAE, and using EasyNegative embedding, CLIP Skip 2, (except for titular image, see comment). Inpaint examples are txt2img with 1 single inpaint done on eyes.
